          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-violet-400 block mb-3">[[journal-extraction]]</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground text-sm mb-1.5">Journal extraction</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            Promote raw daily reflections into lasting notes without losing provenance.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-background p-6 hover:bg-card transition-colors">
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-violet-400 block mb-3">[[vault-search]]</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground text-sm mb-1.5">Vault search</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
