        </p>
        <a
          href="https://reclaw.sh"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 border border-violet-500/40 bg-violet-500/10 text-violet-300 font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg hover:bg-violet-500/20 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5"
